* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
* @semanticintent/recall-ui — footer.rcpy
*
* ACCEPTS:
*   FOOTER-TEXT — scalar — copyright / tagline text
* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
COMPONENT DIVISION.
   DEFINE SITE-FOOTER.
      ACCEPTS FOOTER-TEXT.
      DISPLAY FOOTER
         WITH TEXT FOOTER-TEXT
         WITH ALIGN CENTER.
   END DEFINE.
